## 📐 Key Equations

**Intersection over Union (IoU)**
IoU = |B_pred ∩ B_gt| / |B_pred ∪ B_gt|

**Average Precision (11-point)**
AP = (1/11) Σ max precision at recall r ∈ {0, 0.1, ..., 1}

**Mean Average Precision**
mAP = (1/C) Σ AP_c

